{"tid":2105750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華爾街日報：美國在港問題受限 攻擊聯匯傷盟友 制裁官員影響微","createTime":"2020-07-13T00:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T04:28:43.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5b00f98f7adb7efcdafcbae7f3302ccfa39251","tid":2105750,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T00:35:34.000Z","msg":"報道指美國在香港問題對華行動選項有限<br />\n最後更新時間 2020-07-13 07:33<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報道，美國政府正權衡就香港最近情況向中方採取行動的有限選項，認為如果針對香港的金融體系，有可能損害美國，西方和香港的公司及消費者，因為攻擊聯匯制度，在短期內並非選項；目前較有可能的，是一系列有針對性的制裁，對象包括一些中國中層官員，但華府官員亦擔心，如果袛是制裁更多中方官員及對香港製品採取貿易措施，將難以影響北京將香港融入內地的政治及安全體系。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息人士指，華府官員上星期四在白宮討論有關香港的計劃，並會在今個星期初再開會，可能會宣布制裁或其他措施。白宮拒絕置評。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346733\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2346733&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=0f11b5c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346733</a>"},{"pid":"c2c29b2a040cbf8c910826900c5eee3079adb458","tid":2105750,"uid":74622,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T00:51:00.000Z","msg":"Wall Street係侵侵死對頭之一<br />\nFake news <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c153f52fe23c818a3ee3b5ffa8fd2cee8ed6f0f4","tid":2105750,"uid":16109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T00:58:19.000Z","msg":"最傷應該係wall street<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8da6ec4dc5b31fd7c2402bb89386589d9cf770","tid":2105750,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T00:58:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c15d9d9314b8be92206b45ccc1f87eb15c6306a","tid":2105750,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T00:59:29.000Z","msg":"Wall Street 就收嗲啦"},{"pid":"e3d895d6579166cf401f9b20dcbaaef995a9120a","tid":2105750,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score